Description: Univention Virtual Machine Manager Daemon
 This package contains the Univention Virtual Machine Manager Daemon
 used to collect informations from a farm of virtualization servers.
 .
 This package also includes the Univention Management Console module
 for managing virtualization servers of an UCS domain.

